title: Ep. - 526 - DEATH OF PRINCESS DIANA AND DODI AL FAYED HILARY SHEPERD DISCUSSES HER PREMONITION OF AL FAYED’S DEATH
description:
Kate discusses The Princess (HBO) about the life and death of Princess Diana, and The Diana Investigations (Discovery+) about the inquiry into the accident on August 31, 1997 that took the lives of Diana and Dodi Al Fayed.

 

Hilary Sheperd discusses her friendship with Dodi Al Fayed, what he said about his relationship with Diana, and how she shared with him a premonition of his death.
